{
  "stem": "14687.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Little knives they put in the bread--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to help you running away when they stop the train-- to cut the train pieces, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then [INAUDIBLE] through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we didn't leave the family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, after-- after a few-- it was a week or two weeks, I don't remember--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, plenty.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, plenty.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the ladies, they were expecting, also-- I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, in my-- in my train there, nobody died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Plenty, they were fainting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the other trains, you know, the people they had-- people that were expecting, people, old people-- I think-- I knew a man they throw him in the sea.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Near [INAUDIBLE], you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Levy.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one, he died in Athens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], he died there with the heats.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But all that was, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we arrive in Auschwitz, it was in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were so happy to-- oh, thank god, we arrive to stretch our legs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we saw so many people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all [INAUDIBLE], what do you call these, uh--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 173,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SPANISH]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The fence, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, when we were there, we were happy there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, in the meantime, there were the Germans, the SS, with the dogs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they should take one from here, one from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my auntie said, come with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Help me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my sister, she passed already with the young people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The one, she died there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She said, Lucia, come this way!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Come this way!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when I went, the other German saw me arrive from the-- that line, at there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He hit me in the face, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I was happy with them, with my sister, the three of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
